column5: nice way to show your brother a great time. good report...

excellent report !!! I love fishing with my Bro too.We spend half the time remebering dad taking us fishing when we were kids. Nice Chrome.Goes to show you, you dont need a 1000 buck setup to catch good fish.
sounds like a good day!  a 20lber?  WOW!  although that fish would look a lot nicer in that picture if it wasn't covered in debris!
Nice fish man. You got a knack for catching steel apparently.
